    </thing>
  <thing id="ioUmEleGlo" name="Electroshock Glove" description="{b}Description{/b}\nThis heavy gauntlet is laced with copper wire and can be used to deliver a {i}shocking grasp{/i} 3 times per day that inflicts nonlethal electricity damage. However, this shock can also jolt a creature to its senses, granting a new saving throw to remove one of the following conditions (if more than one is present, determine randomly): confused, dazed, fascinated, frightened, panicked, shaken, staggered, or stunned. An {i}electroshock glove{/i} cannot affect instantaneous or permanent conditions, nor effects that do not allow a saving throw. An {i}electroshock glove{/i} causes no damage to a creature with the dying condition but allows an immediate stabilization roll with a +4 bonus." compset="Wondrous" summary="This heavy gauntlet is laced with copper wire and can be used to deliver a {i}shocking grasp{/i} 3 times per day that inflicts nonlethal electricity damage.">
