  <thing id="ioUmGhoSha" name="Ghost Shackles" description="{b}Description{/b}\nThese rune-carved manacles are enchanted to bind the ectoplasm of ghostly creatures. While they have no enhancement bonus, the {i}ghost shackles{/i} can be used as an improvised weapon that inflicts full damage against incorporeal creatures. In addition, once per day a creature can make a touch attack against an incorporeal creature with the {i}ghost shackles{/i}. If the attack hits, the target is entangled, and as long as the wielder holds onto the {i}ghost shackles{/i} the incorporeal creature is anchored to the spot, unable to move. If the wielder drops the {i}ghost shackles{/i}, the creature may move but retains the entangled condition; the {i}ghost shackles{/i} move with the creature but remain solid, preventing it from moving through or into solid objects or creatures. A creature bound by {i}ghost shackles{/i} may attempt a DC 14 Reflex save as a full-round action to escape." compset="Wondrous" summary="These rune-carved manacles are enchanted to bind the ectoplasm of ghostly creatures.">
